## Introduction

After moving out from my lovely home to a student flat without a dryer, I was always drying to optimise the drying in cold and dry Germany. A problem I did not have for the last 5 years living in Australia.

In this article, I will describe the physics behind drying your clothes and how to dry them the fastest. 

## What is temperature and why do clothes dry?

